  "detailed_description": "<h1>Also recommended for you</h1><p><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431190/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1688654212\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431190/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1688654212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431190/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1688654212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>VIDEO REVIEWS</h1><p><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>Do you have good memory?</strong><br>Observe the scene for a few seconds and memorize the position of the items. Avoid obstacles and collect all carrots.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431190/extras/0c9dfe2fd4beb3cb9383e4f6f14bf861.poster.avif?t=1688654212\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431190/extras/0c9dfe2fd4beb3cb9383e4f6f14bf861.webm?t=1688654212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431190/extras/0c9dfe2fd4beb3cb9383e4f6f14bf861.mp4?t=1688654212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>About the game</strong><br>Bunny's Trail is a colorful 3D Puzzle game, navigate a little rabbit and go through the safe path to collect all the hidden carrots. Enjoy this cute and relaxing game for all ages.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431190/extras/f10b0f4a2c1a6f6767f10fb190ab1392.poster.avif?t=1688654212\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431190/extras/f10b0f4a2c1a6f6767f10fb190ab1392.webm?t=1688654212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431190/extras/f10b0f4a2c1a6f6767f10fb190ab1392.mp4?t=1688654212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>50 Levels<br></li><li>Simple Controls<br></li><li>Original soundtracks<br></li><li>Partial Controller Support<br></li><li>Cute and colorful graphics</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431190/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1688654212\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431190/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1688654212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431190/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1688654212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1431190/extras/7b012bac6042f6238e85a6935ce37b5b.avif?t=1688654212\" width=368 height=260 /></span>",
